<strong><a href="http://www.refugeeaidapp.com/">The Refugee Aid App</a></strong> p<a href="https://www.gnucoop.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/www.refugeeaidapp.com-.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-1811 alignleft" src="https://www.gnucoop.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/www.refugeeaidapp.com--293x300.jpg" alt="www.refugeeaidapp.com-" width="230" height="236" /></a>rovides a single point for refugees to find information, connection and support and a single point for NGOs and charities to share their resources with refugees - location based.
A web based content management and communication system will allow charities and NGOs to get their critical aid to where it is most urgently needed.

